name: SOS 5.5.2 Release
body:
Available in [Maven Central](https://search.maven.org/search?q=g:org.n52.sensorweb-server.sos%20and%20v:5.5.2).

## Change Log
* None

### Dependency Updates
* Bump version.springframework from 5.3.21 to 5.3.23 (#1360, #1455)
* Bump version.arctic-sea from 9.6.0 to 9.9.0 (#1373, #1406, #1443)
* Bump mysql-connector-java from 8.0.29 to 8.0.30 (#1375)
* Bump version.geotools from 27.0 to 27.2 (#1378, #1485)
* Bump Saxon-HE from 11.3 to 11.4 (#1379)
* Bump byte-buddy from 1.12.12 to 1.12.18 (#1382, #1414, #1447, #1463, #1479)
* Bump postgresql from 42.4.0 to 42.5.0 (#1385, #1408, #1416)
* Bump mssql-jdbc from 11.1.2.jre8-preview to 11.2.1.jre8 (#1388, #1448)
* Bump version.springframework.security from 5.7.2 to 5.7.3 (#1395)
* Bump version.slf4j from 1.7.36 to 2.0.3 (#1411, #1453, #1465, #1475)
* Bump version.elasticsearch from 7.17.5 to 7.17.6 (#1417)
* Bump joda-time from 2.11.0 to 2.12.0 (#1421, #1470, #1482)
* Bump ojdbc8 from 21.6.0.0.1 to 21.7.0.0 (#1424)
* Bump version.hibernate from 5.6.10.Final to 5.6.12.Final (#1433, #1472)
* Bump janino from 3.1.7 to 3.1.8 (#1435)
* Bump spotbugs-annotations from 4.7.1 to 4.7.2 (#1436)
* Bump jackson-bom from 2.13.3 to 2.13.4 (#1437)
* Bump mockito-core from 4.7.0 to 4.8.1 (#1445, #1486)
* Bump jetty-maven-plugin from 11.0.11 to 11.0.12 (#1456)
* Bump maven-jar-plugin from 3.2.2 to 3.3.0 (#1459)
* Bump jettison from 1.5.0 to 1.5.1 (#1468)
* Bump geolatte-geom from 1.8.2 to 1.9.0 (#1477)

### Breaking Changes
* None

See [here](https://github.com/52North/sos/compare/v5.5.1...v5.5.2) for the complete commit log.
